#hm-note[
  Month 6 concludes Quarter II. The Tarot deepens from a correspondence table
  into a living diagnostic instrument. The Tree of Life moves from theory to
  personal mapping. The pedagogical goal is genuine integration of the symbolic
  framework with the student's actual life and Work — not intellectual fluency
  with the system. A student who can recite all the sephirothic attributions
  but cannot map their own Plant Stone onto the Tree has not yet done Month 6's
  real work. Press for personal application, not performance.
]

