= ⬡ QUARTER II GATHERING — The Philosophic Mercury

*Theme:* Astrological election work shared; comparative water preparations; Year One review spreads.

#hm-note[
  This gathering has more content than most — the alchemical almanacs, water
  preparations, and Tarot spreads each warrant sharing time. Keep to roughly equal
  time per student; use the Tarot spreads to close the session as they often open
  unexpected depth.
]

*Students share:*
- Their personal alchemical calendar for the year: one or two key elected moments
  explained.
- Their natal chart reading: which planet dominates their constitution and what
  this means for their laboratory tendencies.
- Their water preparations in current state: comparison of fermented distillates,
  cohobated rain, and dew preparations.
- Their Year One review Tarot spread: what the cards showed about the plant work.

